OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be another dry and
OL,6,Fbright day with long periods of
OL,7,Fsunshine. A chilly and somewhat cloudy
OL,8,Fstart for many, then becoming warm by
OL,9,Fthe afternoon.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FDry with some evening
OL,12,Fsunshine to start with, leading to
OL,13,Fclear spells overnight. Patchy fog or
OL,14,Ffrost may develop inland overnight.
OL,15,
OL,16,CSaturday:FIt will be another dry day
OL,17,Fwith plenty of sunshine though a bit
OL,18,Fmore cloud than previous days. Warm
OL,19,Fagain in the west, but a bit cooler
OL,20,Faround Greater Glasgow.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
