OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FBright
OL,6,Fspells and variable cloud on Sunday
OL,7,Fand Monday with the chance of a few
OL,8,Fshowers. Dry with sunny spells again
OL,9,FTuesday, warmer in the west.
